  "text": "Audit stack clash protection in GCC. Find: 1. The prologue expansion in gcc/config/i386/i386.cc (ix86_expand_prologue) which integrates stack clash probing on x86. 2. anti_adjust_stack_and_probe_stack_clash in gcc/explow.cc -- the generic stack clash probe loop. 3. TARGET_STACK_CLASH_PROTECTION_ALLOCA_PROBE_RANGE target hook in gcc/target.def. 4. Test file gcc/testsuite/gcc.target/i386/stack-clash-protection.c validating the feature. 5. -fstack-clash-protection option definition in gcc/common.opt.",
